brownforman – michael todman nominated to serve on bf board previous next michael todman nominated to serve on bf board louisville ky june   – brownforman corporation nyse bfa bfb announced today that michael a todman has agreed to stand for election to the company’s board of directors  brownforman’s annual shareholders’ meeting is july  and class a stockholders will vote on a slate of  directors including  incumbent directors in addition to todman todman is the president of whirlpool corporation and has served on whirlpool’s board of directors since   he joined whirlpool in  and has served in a variety of financial sales marketing new product development and leadership roles over the course of his career  prior to joining whirlpool todman held leadership positions at wang laboratories and price waterhouse and co  todman currently serves on the board of directors of newellrubbermaid  a native of st thomas us virgin islands and the son of a career diplomat todman has lived andor worked in north and subsaharan africa the middle east latin america and europe  he is a graduate of georgetown university brownforman board chairman geo garvin brown iv said “mike todman is a true internationalist with extensive consumer product experience and a proven track record as an executive leader  we look forward to his election this july at our annual shareholders’ meeting and know that he will be an excellent asset to our board and help contribute to our company’s future success”  for more than  years brownforman corporation has enriched the experience of life by responsibly building fine quality beverage alcohol brands including jack daniel’s tennessee whiskey jack daniel’s tennessee honey southern comfort finlandia jack daniel’s  cola canadian mist korbel gentleman jack el jimador herradura sonomacutrer chambord new mix tuaca and woodford reserve  brownforman’s brands are supported by nearly  employees and sold in approximately  countries worldwide  for more information about the company please visit httpwwwbrownformancom   tjune th corporate share this story choose your platform click here for financial reports recent news brownforman reports fiscal  results expects stronger trends to continue in fiscal  brownforman recognized as best for vets employers  list military times ranking lists spirits maker kathleen gutmann elected to brownforman board of directors brownforman’s fourth quarter earnings release and conference call scheduled for june   brownforman declares cash dividend archives june  may  march  february  january  december  november  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  september  august  july  june  may  march  january  december  november  october  september  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  october  september  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  september  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  october  september  august  july  june  may  march  february  january  december  november  october  september  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  september  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  october  september  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  november  october  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  october  september  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  october  september  august  july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  october  september  august  july  june  may  march  february  january  categories all brand corporate corporate responsibility earnings michael todman sees a world…  the herald palladium  localnews close michael todman sees a world…  the herald palladium  localnews advanced search ° broken clouds home eedition about us contact us online f